<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="variation-n">variation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌveəri'eɪʃn/    美 /ˌveri'eɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>变化；差别：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the seasonal variation 
季节性变化</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After all, there is probably as much <strong>variation of</strong> pronunciation within the two countries as between them. 
毕竟，两个国家各自内部的口音差别可能跟两国之间的口音差别一样大。</p><footer>外研⑤-1</footer></div></div>